title: 07/08/21 DPS Hour 3 Gina Mizell
itunes:title: 07/08/21 DPS Hour 3 Gina Mizell
description:
Jason Smith and Ryan Hollins, in for Dan, react to Johnny Juzang returning to UCLA and explain how this relates to Name, Image, and Likeness in the NCAA. The guys break down what the Bucks need to do to stop Chris Paul. Suns Insider for NBA.com Gina Mizell stops by to give all the insight on the Suns ahead of Game 2. Plus, a special surprise guest stops by for the closing minutes of the show!
